&lt;td&gt;First build failed after 1 hour&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Linuxdev (Windows host)&lt;br&gt;8GB , i7 4 cores&lt;/td&gt;
